<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>The Common Room — Secret Society of Strangers</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('components/nav') %>
    <main class="document">
      <div class="board-header">
        <h1 class="title">The Common Room</h1>
        <a href="/new" class="compose-link">Leave a Word</a>
      </div>
      <p class="subtitle" style="margin-bottom: 8px">
        Words left by those who have passed through
      </p>

      <!--
      LOGIC NOTE (remove this comment in the real templated version):
      Swap the banner below between guest / member states depending on req.user.
      .status-banner            → logged in, not a member
      .status-banner--member    → logged in member or admin
      Omit entirely when logged out.
    -->
      <span class=" status-banner status-banner--member">&#10046; Recognized Member</span>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <ul class="entry-list">
        <li class="entry">
          <div class="entry__meta">
            <span class="entry__author">M. Faircloth</span>
            <span aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
            <time datetime="2026-06-14">14 June 1826</time>
          </div>
          <h2 class="entry__title">On the Matter of the Third Floor</h2>
          <p class="entry__body">
            Let it be known that the door at the end of the corridor remains
            locked for good reason. Those who ask twice will not be asked a
            third time.
          </p>
          <button class="entry__delete" type="button">Remove</button>
        </li>

        <li class="entry">
          <div class="entry__meta">
            <span class="entry__author entry__author--sealed"
              >Hidden Stranger</span
            >
            <span aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
            <time datetime="2026-06-12">12 June 1826</time>
          </div>
          <h2 class="entry__title">A Warning, Kindly Meant</h2>
          <p class="entry__body">
            Not all who knock are friends. Verify the seal before you open. This
            is the last courtesy I will extend on the subject.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li class="entry">
          <div class="entry__meta">
            <span class="entry__author">R. Voss</span>
            <span aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
            <time datetime="2026-06-09">9 June 1826</time>
          </div>
          <h2 class="entry__title">Found: One Glove, Left Hand</h2>
          <p class="entry__body">
            Discovered beneath the reading table after Thursday's gathering.
            Inquire with the steward if it belongs to you. No questions asked,
            as is our custom.
          </p>
          <button class="entry__delete" type="button">Remove</button>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <!--
      Use this in place of .entry-list when there are no messages yet:
      <div class="empty-state">No words have been left. Be the first to break the silence.</div>
    --></main>
  </body>
</html>
